name: Outpost 1
description: Another quality deathmatch level by me, Marc Bublitz. This one takes place in an outpost. There are several reasons why I particularly like this one: First, I'm kind-of fond of the "Cyber-Attack" ad I've constructed. Secondly, I'm very happy I could get a satisfactory color alignment with one of my ray-traced spaceships. Also, notice the neat gate that I've edited from the MIDBARS texture.
